PrecisConfirmation of a FINAL AGREEMENT between the ANIMBIIGOO ZAAGI'IGAN ANISHINAABEK, the Crown and the Province of Ontario, which identifies some 1270 hectares of provincial Crown land situated in Greenstone, including all surface and subsurface rights, to be set apart as a reserve for the use and benefit of that Band.
